## OS

This repo hosts OS(a custom version of Petalinux), which represents the main camera OS, which is untrusted in ProvCam.
It contains modfied drivers and kernel modules to support the hardware design of ProvCam, such as the built-in replay function, as mentioned in the paper. 

To change the operating mode of ProvCam, please modify the parameter `secure_cam_is_in_tcs_mode`, which you can find at `inlcude/linux/secure_cam.h`. 
Recompilation is required after the modification.
